        <updateDate>2008-06-02T20:41:49Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Fairness in Nursing Home Arbitration Act of 2008 - Provides that a pre-dispute arbitration agreement between a long-term care facility and a resident (or anyone acting on the resident's behalf) shall not be valid or specifically enforceable.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
